<h2 id="upgrading">Upgrading</h2>

<h3 id="4-0">4.0</h3>

<p>If you use Sprockets, update the gem and you’re good to go!</p>

<p>If you use Webpacker, run:</p>

<pre><code class="sh">yarn upgrade chartkick --latest
</code></pre>

<p>If you use Chart.js with Webpacker, also run:</p>

<pre><code class="sh">yarn upgrade chart.js --latest
</code></pre>

<p>And in <code>app/javascript/packs/application.js</code>, change:</p>

<pre><code class="js">require(&quot;chartkick&quot;)
require(&quot;chart.js&quot;)
</code></pre>

<p>to:</p>

<pre><code class="js">require(&quot;chartkick/chart.js&quot;)
</code></pre>

